item.title: About this blog
item.description: This blog will be home to personal musings, and things that I find interesting. It is mostly a record for myself, though you are welcome to peruse. My other work that has a more specific purpose, such as Reckoning In Systems (a blog about systems thinking and city design) may be posted here as well.
